text.paragraph:
Simvastatin is butanoic acid, 2,2-dimethyl-,1,2,3,7,8,8a-hexahydro-3,7-dimethyl-8-[2-(tetrahydro-4-hydroxy-6-oxo-2 H-pyran-2-yl)-ethyl]-1-naphthalenyl ester, [1S-[1α,3α,7β,8β(2S*
                     ,4S*
                     ),-8aβ]]. The molecular formula of simvastatin is C25H38O5 and its molecular weight is 418.57. Its structural formula is:
